snippet.textDisplay:
DRY EYES

SKIN- I have dry-normal skin and have been using the Akar eye serum every night and it makes a huge difference
EYEBALLS- if you're using eye drops, make sure you're NOT using "redness correcting" eye drops. They actually restrict your blood vessels to reduce redness and end up drying out your eyes more. Use a lubricating eye drop instead
snippet.textOriginal:

SKIN- I have dry-normal skin and have been using the Akar eye serum every night and it makes a huge difference
